1.0.name: wordpress/tabgarb
1.0.description:
TabGarb is a WordPress plugin which gives your wordpress a power to change content into Javascript tab enable content very easily, Tabgarb use HTML comment tags in place of using tags like [ (tabs), [tabs] , {tabs} ] which make your content wordpress friendly ( TabGarb Formatting tag will not spoil your content in case TabGarb is not installed in your wordpress ). TabGarb come with editable css theme ( you can edit tabs css from your admin panel easly ) and you can change the speed and effect of changing tab direct from TabGarb Settings in WordPress admin. New feature 2.3 : Add normal Page Load Functionality (using this make your post/page fast load).

More information will be found here

We are continue updating our plugin Thanks for your all support and comments. !

Usage Usage information will be found here
